## Project Overview

Flourishing Souls Foundation is a charity platform designed to support individuals in need, including the poor and the jobless. The platform aims to provide comprehensive support and create opportunities for all. This project will be developed using HTML, JavaScript, CSS, and any additional necessary technologies to ensure robust functionality and an outstanding user experience.

## Platform Features

- **Donations:** Allow users to easily make donations to support the foundation's work.
- **Volunteer Sign-Up:** Users can register to volunteer and become part of our mission by contacting us.
- **Request Support:** Individuals can reach out through the platform to request assistance.
- **Events & Activities:** View updates, upcoming events, and the foundation’s ongoing movements.
- **Impact Gallery:** Showcase all the places, people, and communities we've helped, complete with well-designed images and videos.
- **Contact & Engagement:** Easy ways for users to get in touch or engage with our team.

## Project Structure

- **Full Project Name:** Flourishing Souls Foundation
- **Logo:** Please place the official logo inside the `images` folder.
- **Files & Folders:** The repository will include all the necessary files and directories. Please make sure to maintain the structure as described in the documentation and code.

