I am starting the Flourishing Souls Foundation platform from scratch, and I want a large, production-ready, enterprise-level project with a modern, beautiful, user-centric design inspired by Notion and DropShop. The stack will be based on HTML, JavaScript, and CSS (preferably with TailwindCSS), and must leverage the following:

- **React** (with Vite as the build tool for fast modern development)
- **TailwindCSS** for highly customizable styling
- **JavaScript/TypeScript** for maintainable, scalable code (preferably TypeScript for type safety, but JS is also fine)
- **Paystack** integration for secure donations
- **Supabase** (Postgres+BaaS) for all database needs and authentication (please include fallback/option for Google or Clerk authentication if needed)
- **Optional Node.js/Express backend** for extensibility if/when needed (API/connections/restricted/SSR routes)

