## Installations & Dependencies (Terminal Setup)

### 1. Scaffold the React + Vite + TailwindCSS Project

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/flourishing-souls-foundation.git
cd flourishing-souls-foundation
npm create vite@latest . -- --template react
npm install
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwindcss init -p
```

### 2. Install Required Dependencies

```bash
npm install react-router-dom axios @supabase/supabase-js
npm install @headlessui/react @heroicons/react
npm install @paystack/paystack-js
# Typescript support (optional)
npm install --save typescript @types/react @types/node
# For Google or Clerk Auth (if needed)
npm install @clerk/clerk-react @clerk/clerk-sdk@next
npm install @react-oauth/google
```

### 3. Configure Tailwind and Supabase/Env

- Fill out `.env` files for Supabase and Paystack keys.
- Set up Tailwind in `tailwind.config.js` and `src/styles/tailwind.css`.

### 4. Run Development Server

```bash
npm run dev
```

### 5. (If Backend Required)
```bash
cd backend
npm init -y
npm install express cors dotenv
# Optional: Add more as needed, e.g. nodemon, mongoose, etc
node server.js
```

